{"tid":1871793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO喊話更名 CNN不甩仍稱「武漢冠狀病毒」","createTime":"2020-02-09T16:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T18:05:53.000Z","uid":3189,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2b6e3a23c983d6b9f12c67996b98260cce06a9","tid":1871793,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕世界衛生組織（WHO）呼籲應以「2019-nCOV（novel coronavirus）acute respiratory disease」，亦即「2019-nCoV急性呼吸道疾病」來稱呼目前的新型冠狀病毒疫情，別再和地名扯上關係，但《CNN》對此無視，目前仍以「武漢冠狀病毒（Wuhan coronavirus）」稱之。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》在報導武漢肺炎死亡人數已超過嚴重急性呼吸道症候群（SARS）時，直接使用「武漢冠狀病毒」一詞。2003年的SARS疫情共有8000多人感染、774人死亡，但目前全球的武漢冠狀病毒感染，在全球已有3萬7554個確診病例、813人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》指出，與SARS一樣，這次的疫情是由冠狀病毒引起的，冠狀病毒是一種常見的動物傳染病毒，症狀從普通感冒到更嚴重的疾病症狀都有，例如中東呼吸症候群（MERS）也是其中的一種。<br />\n<br />\n更有甚者，《CNN》還直接寫明「SARS和武漢（SARS and Wuhan）的疫情爆發均始於中國」，等同於把「武漢」當成這次疫情的替代用詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3062377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3062377&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=250e66cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3062377&h=11ccd01b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3062377</a>"},{"pid":"bfe792dd66ac310a5576f6be43e67ec15fbcc40e","tid":1871793,"uid":51621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"SARS和武漢（SARS and Wuhan）的疫情爆發均始於中國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a45b36f8b3591abc9f40bfd15a0d288b61c6985","tid":1871793,"uid":242537,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkX9sTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http